{"type": "article", "id": 2774, "title": "George Sowden 瓷质茶壶", "description": "", "date": "2014-10-11T07:50:53Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232538flcLkPKJ02g1C4ra.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t就像有人嫌弃速溶咖啡一样，许多茶饮爱好者也不满意茶包泡出来的茶。为此，来自意大利的 George Sowden 带来了三款瓷质茶壶设计，壶身的形状极为简洁，亮点在于一个拥有超过 160000 个小孔的圆筒形过滤器，这些布满过滤器四周及底部的微型孔使茶叶在冲泡过程中充分舒展开来，茶渣则通通留在了过滤器内。这三款茶具定价 58.5 －68.5 英镑不等，<a href=\"http://sowdenshop.com/index.php?id_category=4&amp;controller=category&amp;id_lang=1\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052325362SQZaMJDru5XGUL4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052325366W0sbophdgZBDMGN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232537DzRQLXhF9yn2ocbM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232537ryLRHXNclVPAgnqM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052325371t5FXvPJpksrKWmi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}